      "This framework contrasts with linear educational models, which follow fixed sequences for all students.": {},
      "The modular structure is created by identifying core competencies and building assessment tools for each.": {
        "This partitioning can be recursive, creating sub-modules for specialized knowledge areas.": {},
        "Different educational theories, like constructivism or mastery learning, can inform the design.": {}
      }
    },
    "The initial platform, EduFlex, implements this through learning objects and adaptive assessment engines.": {
      "It sequences content using prerequisite relationships to maintain logical progression.": {},
      "The system's objectives include maximizing engagement, minimizing frustration, and ensuring knowledge retention.": {
        "Machine learning algorithms analyze performance patterns to customize learning paths.": {}
      }
    },
    "A significant student benefit is the capacity to focus learning on specific knowledge gaps.": {
      "Learners begin with diagnostic assessments to identify current proficiency levels.": {},
      "They can then navigate to targeted modules addressing particular skill deficiencies.": {
